products.title: ASUS ROG Strix AMD Radeon RX 5700XT Overclocked 8G GDDR6 HDMI DisplayPort Gaming Graphics Card (ROG-STRIX-RX5700XT-O8G-GAMING)

Supports up-to 6 monitors with 3x DisplayPort 1. 4 and 1x HDMI 2. 0B port
Pci Express 4. 0 delivers double the bandwidth with throughput up to 16 gt/s

products.description: Powered by AMD Radeon with PCI 4. 0 performance, the ROG Strix RX 5700XT O8G Gaming Graphics Card features a reinforced frame, customizable Aura Sync RGB lighting, increased cooling performance from triple Axial-Tech fans and Max Contact technology. See every rich detail in 5K at 120Hz with DisplayPort 1. 4 with DSC.
